</taxonomicName>
, non-type Ơ (
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FDD0F938704FF897" box="[601,636,1786,1807]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">1–6</emphasis>
) and ♀ (
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FD5CF9387137F897" box="[725,772,1786,1807]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">7–11</emphasis>
) (Nigeria, USNM): 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FC40F93871DFF897" box="[969,1004,1786,1807]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">1–2</emphasis>
— genitalia, right and ventral view; 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FEA1F8D67300F8B1" box="[296,307,1812,1833]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">3</emphasis>
— outer and inner surstyli, ventral view; 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FD4EF8D670D9F8B1" box="[711,746,1812,1833]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">4–6</emphasis>
— phallus glans at different angles; 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FBC0F8D77667F8B2" box="[1097,1108,1813,1834]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">7</emphasis>
— oviscape apex; 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FF57F8ED72DAF8DC" box="[222,233,1839,1860]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">8</emphasis>
