<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FED4F8ED735BF8DC" box="[349,360,1839,1860]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">9</emphasis>
— vagina and ventral receptacle; 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDC3345FD22F8ED70F1F8DC" box="[683,706,1839,1860]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="199">10</emphasis>
