</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="0A950EFFFFDD3344FF27FC0170CDFB96" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6453696" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6453696" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6453696/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="200" startId="5.[174,207,963,985]" targetBox="[299,1059,176,942]" targetPageId="5">
<paragraph id="5E555E77FFDD3344FF27FC0170CDFB96" blockId="5.[174,1233,961,1038]" pageId="5" pageNumber="200">
Fig. 4. 
<taxonomicName id="99EA25F4FFDD3344FF7BFC01738AFC40" box="[242,441,963,984]" class="Insecta" family="Pyrgotidae" genus="Campylocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="200" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="uniclor">
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDD3344FF7BFC01738AFC40" box="[242,441,963,984]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="200">Campylocera uniclor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
syntype Ơ (MHNP): 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDD3344FD06FC0170A9FC40" box="[655,666,963,984]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="200">1</emphasis>
— habitus, lateral view; 
<emphasis id="6C9E8265FFDD3344FC19FC0171A8FC40" box="[912,923,963,984]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="200">2</emphasis>
